  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the VIVID-1 data collection study is to establish a database of clinical
      images and associated technical files from commercial cases using the Visualase Thermal
      Therapy System (VTTS). All data collected will be de-identified. No safety or effectiveness
      assessments will be completed.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
